(2) In these Regulations a reference to a numbered Article without 

qualification is to an Article so numbered of the Interbus Agreement. 

(3) A word or expression which is used in these Regulations and is also 
used in the Interbus Agreement has, unless the contrary intention appears, the 
same meaning in these Regulations that it has in the Interbus Agreement.
